{"tid":2005280,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"加拿大CBC News染紅 批評大紀元報導不實及歧視中國人","createTime":"2020-05-07T04:08:36.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-08T04:11:46.000Z","uid":116146,"like":28,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":31,"replies":[{"pid":"c144e14fda0775cd306de32909514bdd49adfedb","tid":2005280,"uid":116146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-07T04:08:36.000Z","msg":"事源係咁嘅 <br />\n大紀元係加拿大有派發英文版報紙<br />\n其中一篇文章就話武漢肺炎疑似從中國實驗室洩漏<br />\n但冇講過病毒係中國嘅生化武器<br />\n但係CBC News竟然訪問左啲人去批評大紀元<br />\n指控病毒係中國嘅生化武器呢一句係歧視加不實<br />\n片段upload咗上YouTube之後comment好多人都批評CBC News<br />\n結果CBC News竟然關閉咗comment<br />\n冇幾耐仲將video del 咗<br />\n最過癮嘅係隔咗一陣CBC News又搵其他人拍返差唔多嘅video<br />\nCBC news 差唔多可以話係加拿大嘅國營media<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n詳情可以睇<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/GNOmP7auk_0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FGNOmP7auk_0&d=w9JnFmhD9tlFtzSpwKDBdTsyqOHkMMjDRpVYVMaq87A%3D&h=f431a5c1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/GNOmP7auk_0</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">所以大家真係要打下Twitter 戰線 <br />\n話比全世界知中國想脫罪</span></span>"},{"pid":"ff03a9ccc265b49d0d0146b0d690f68002102caa","tid":2005280,"uid":66087,"like":30,"dislike":0,"score":30,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-05-07T04:14:33.000Z","msg":"大紀元唔識玩<br />\n<br />\n拎份睇就知道，成份野陰謀論味道太重，而且有d內容神神怪怪，鼓吹法輪功<br />\n<br />\n好難入主流"},{"pid":"fed9145b835883977ca8446a19d1998fa47e0261","tid":2005280,"uid":117276,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-07T04:29:29.000Z","msg":"支那大"},{"pid":"f14a7d6bda881d9531fd118bb272b6ebb375d0d9","tid":2005280,"uid":3149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-07T05:51:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a0381980921d6c13b4533343da21a787b96703d","tid":2005280,"uid":26752,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score